Feature: Bowling Kata
	As a Player
	I want to play some bowling
	To have some fun with my friends!
	
Scenario: Worst game ever
	Given I have a new game
	When I miss all the pins in every single frame
	Then the score should be the lowest
	
Scenario: A perfect score
	Given I have a new game
	When I do a strike on every frame
	Then the score should be the highest
	

Scenario: A bunch of average games
	Given I have a new game
	When I roll a game of "9, 0, 3, 7, 6, 1, 3, 7, 8, 1, 5, 5, 0, 10, 8, 0, 7, 3, 8, 2, 8"
	Then the score is 131
